						<summary>

						<p>The inscription is damaged. It seems to register a gift of a village (by the chief) for the expenses of worship to god Mīnākshi Sundarēśvarar at Kīḻaikkarai <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Niṉaittadu-muḍitta-Vināyakar-paṭṭiṇam.</p>						

